The agenda looks as follows:


18h00 - 18h30: Welcome, Pizza and drinks


18h30 - 18h45: <bold>OWASP Update</bold> (by Sebastien Deleersnyder,
OWASP BeLux)


18h45 - 19h00: <bold> ISSA Intro</bold>(by Tomas Vanhoof, ISSA)


19h00 - 20h00: <bold>Operational security impact on developing secure
